To get the next LOD level from a given LOD, you can use the `next` method. This method increments the current LOD value by 1 and returns the new LOD. Here is the code example: 

```zig
pub inline fn next(self: Lod) Lod {
	return @enumFromInt(@intFromEnum(self) + 1);
}
